TWComponent.script: tw.local.sqlString select distinct lugx.group_id as groupID, lugx.group_name as groupNAme, decode(lugx.group_type, 3, 'BPM', 0, 'External', 'Unknown') as groupType from BPM_USR_RUNTIME_PROPS burp, LSW_USR_XREF lux, LSW_USR_GRP_MEM_XREF lugmx, lsw_usr_grp_xref lugx where BURP.USER_ID(+) = LUX.USER_ID and lux.user_id = lugmx.user_id and lugx.group_id = lugmx.group_id and lux.user_id = ? and lugx.group_type != 1 order by lugx.group_id
